I'm Siobhan Roberts.

00:00:04.910 --> 00:00:08.250
And I am John Horton
Conway's biographer.

00:00:08.250 --> 00:00:10.935
JOHN HORTON CONWAY: And
I'm that person mentioned.

00:00:10.935 --> 00:00:12.446
SIOBHAN ROBERTS:
John Horton Conway.

