00:25:37.970 --> 00:25:46.390
contentious among
physicists that if we have

00:25:46.390 --> 00:25:49.250
free will-- that is to
say human experimenters

00:25:49.250 --> 00:25:51.000
have a little bit of free will.

00:25:51.000 --> 00:25:53.230
They don't have
to have very much.

00:25:53.230 --> 00:25:55.630
That so do elementary
particles have

00:25:55.630 --> 00:25:58.880
