and see that two ones, then

00:35:16.060 --> 00:35:19.650
the third direction you know
is a zero without looking.

00:35:19.650 --> 00:35:23.305
Equally, if you see a one and a
zero for two of the directions,

00:35:23.305 --> 00:35:24.680
you know that the
third direction

00:35:24.680 --> 00:35:26.634
is a one without looking.

00:35:26.634 --> 00:35:27.550
So those are certain--

00:35:27.550 --> 00:35:29.320
Oh, look, there is-- sorry.

